& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is pressure impact ThinkAbout record drafting
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_pressure_impact_thinkabout_record
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 10
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, copy-exact overclaim, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_PressureImpactThinkAboutRecord] is the active semantic stack frame for drafting a deeper pressure impact ThinkAbout record
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_pressure_impact_thinkabout_record
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_pressure_impact_pilot_candidate
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, pressure_impact_pilot_review, accepted_worker_proposal, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_016, ThinkAbout_record, outside_boundary, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is pressure_impact_thinkabout_review_016.sop, pressure_impact_thinkabout_result_016_retry_001.sop, lmstudio_limited_worker_pilot_queue_001.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_016.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is draft deeper ThinkAbout record from accepted worker proposal
  + [question_register] is how to convert proposal evidence into a Codex-authored record without granting worker integration authority
  + [delineation_register] is inside accepted retry, Codex review, local task-fit latch, pressure signal, impact signal, evidence, proposal, outside, and next drafting target
  + [periphery_register] is broad competence outside, direct trust outside, worker mutation outside, external examples outside, automatic launch outside, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is synthesize_record, preserve_sources, cite_worker_proposal, preserve_outside, validate_record, emit_next_tick
  + [evidence_register] is accepted retry output, pilot review, worker latch source, and operating_loop_tick_016
  + [wisdom_register] is the accepted proposal can seed a useful Codex-authored ThinkAbout record if source and caution remain visible
  + [caution_register] is the first attempt proved plausible foreign examples can pass format validation, so local task fit must remain active
  + [balance_register] is stable because integration remains a Codex-authored drafting step
  + [integration_register] is worker proposal accepted, deeper record pending Codex drafting
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

(current_attention_runtime_registry_state) :active_root_frame: /semantic_register_set and return_anchor/ |registry_outside|
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_pressure_impact_thinkabout_record
  + [semantic_register_set] is focus, question, delineation, periphery, operation, evidence, Wisdom, Caution, balance, and integration registers
  + [return_anchor] is CurrentFocalPoint
  |registry_outside| hidden model state, executable runtime stack, unreviewed worker authority, unrelated dirty files, and untracked cognition

